\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs79\f1\fs32\insrsid9846478\charrsid9846478 Unto Thee have I lifted up mine eyes, unto Thee that dwellest in heaven.
\par 
\par Behold, as the eyes of servants look unto the hands of their masters, as the eyes of the handmaid look unto the hands of her mistress, so do our eyes look unto the Lord our God, until He take pity on us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid9846478\charrsid7173770 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs79\f1\fs32\insrsid9846478\charrsid9846478 Have mercy on us, O Lord, have mercy on us, for greatly are we filled with abasement.
\par 
\par Greatly hath our soul been filled therewith; let reproach come upon them that prosper, and abasement on the proud.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\fs32\insrsid9846478\charrsid7173770 
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\s91\qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid9846478 \rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af1\afs32\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\i\f1\fs32\cf6\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
