\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\qj \li0\ri0\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid9846478 \rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs24\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af1\afs32 
\ltrch\fcs0 \cs79\f1\fs32\insrsid9846478\charrsid9846478 Had it not been that the Lord was with us, let Israel now say, had it not been that the Lord was with us, When men rose up against us, then had they swallowed us up alive.
\par 
\par When their wrath raged against us, then had the water overwhelmed us.
\par 
\par Our soul hath passed through a torrent; then had our soul passed through the water that is irresistible.
\par 
\par Blessed be the Lord Who hath not given us to be a prey to their teeth.
\par 
\par Our soul like a sparrow was delivered out of the snare of the hunters.
\par 
\par The snare is broken, and we are delivered.
\par 
\par Our help is in the name of the Lord, Who hath made heaven and the earth.
\par }\pard\plain \ltrpar\s60\qc \li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid9846478 \rtlch\fcs1 \ab\ai\af1\afs32\alang1025 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\i\f1\fs32\cf6\lang1024\langfe1024\cgrid\noproof\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\rtlch\fcs1 
